COMPONENT NAME: CKM Netezza
AUTHOR: Oracle
DESCRIPTION - Check Knowledge Module for Netezza - This module controls the validity of the constraints of a Datastore and rejects the invalid records in an error table. It can be used for static controls as well as flow controls
OPTIONS (Refer to Option descriptions for more information on each option) - DROP_ERROR_TABLE: When this option is set to YES, the error table will be dropped each time a control is performed on the target table. This means that any rejected records, identified and stored during previous control operations, will be lost. - DROP_CHECK_TABLE: When this option is set to YES, the SNP_CHECK_TAB check table (which is created in the default Physical Schema of the Physical Server that hosts the controlled table) will be dropped each time a control is performed on the target table. This table contains a collection of all rejected records retrieved from all datastores hosted on the same Physical Server (whatever the Physical Schema may be). - UPGRADE_ERROR_TABLE: When this option is set to YES, the existing E$ table will be upgraded to the new E$ table structure.

When this option is set to YES, the error table will be dropped each time a control is performed on the target table. This means that any rejected records, identified and stored during previous control operations, will be lost.

When this option is set to YES, the SNP_CHECK_TAB check table (which is created in the default Physical Schema of the Physical Server that hosts the controlled table) will be dropped each time a control is performed on the target table. This table contains a collection of all rejected records retrieved from all datastores hosted on the same Physical Server (whatever the Physical Schema may be).
When this option is set to YES, the existing E$ table and check tables will be dropped and recreate.
insert check sum into check table

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","CHECK_NAME", "W")%> ( CATALOG_NAME, SCHEMA_NAME, RESOURCE_NAME, FULL_RES_NAME, ERR_TYPE, ERR_MESS, CHECK_DATE, ORIGIN, CONS_NAME, CONS_TYPE, ERR_COUNT ) select '<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("CATALOG")%>', '<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("SCHEMA")%>', '<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_NAME")%>', '<%=odiRef.getTable("L","TARG_NAME","D")%>', E.ODI_ERR_TYPE, E.ODI_ERR_MESS, E.ODI_CHECK_DATE, E.ODI_ORIGIN, E.ODI_CONS_NAME, E.ODI_CONS_TYPE, count(*) from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> E where E.ODI_ERR_TYPE = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' and E.ODI_ORIGIN = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>' and E.ODI_SESS_NO = '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>' group by E.ODI_ERR_TYPE, E.ODI_ERR_MESS, E.ODI_CHECK_DATE, E.ODI_ORIGIN, E.ODI_CONS_NAME, E.ODI_CONS_TYPE

create table <%=odiRef.getTable("L","CHECK_NAME","W")%> ( CATALOG_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> , SCHEMA_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> , RESOURCE_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, FULL_RES_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ERR_TYPE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "1", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ERR_MESS <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "250", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> , CHECK_DATE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_DATE", "", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ORIGIN <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "250", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, CONS_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "128", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, CONS_TYPE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "2", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ERR_COUNT <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_NUMERIC", "10", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> )

delete from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","CHECK_NAME", "W")%> where CATALOG_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("CATALOG")%>' and SCHEMA_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("SCHEMA")%>' and ORIGIN = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>' and ERR_TYPE = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>'

create table <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_ERR_TYPE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "1", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ODI_ERR_MESS <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "250", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ODI_CHECK_DATE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_DATE", "", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]\t\t[DEST_WRI_DT] " + odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL"), ",\n\t", "", "")%>, ODI_ORIGIN <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "250", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ODI_CONS_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "128", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ODI_CONS_TYPE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "2", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ODI_SESS_NO <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "36", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> ) <%=odiRef.getColList("DISTRIBUTE ON (", "[COL_NAME]", ", ", ")", "PK")%>

delete from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> where (ODI_ERR_TYPE = 'S' and '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' = 'S') or (ODI_ERR_TYPE = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' and ODI_ORIGIN = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>')

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_ERR_TYPE, ODI_ERR_MESS, ODI_ORIGIN, ODI_CHECK_DATE, ODI_CONS_NAME, ODI_CONS_TYPE, ODI_SESS_NO, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> ) select '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=odiRef.getPK("MESS")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=odiRef.getPK("KEY_NAME")%>', 'PK', '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>', <%=odiRef.getColList("", odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS") + ".[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%> where (select count(*) from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","CT_NAME","A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> E where <%=odiRef.getColList("", odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME]=E.[COL_NAME]", "
	and	", "", "PK=1")%> )>1 <%=odiRef.getFilter()%>

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_ERR_TYPE, ODI_ERR_MESS, ODI_ORIGIN, ODI_CHECK_DATE, ODI_CONS_NAME, ODI_CONS_TYPE, ODI_SESS_NO, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> ) select '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=odiRef.getAK("MESS")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=odiRef.getAK("KEY_NAME")%>', 'AK', '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>', <%=odiRef.getColList("", odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS") + ".[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%> , (select <%=odiRef.getAKColList("", "E.[COL_NAME]", ",
		", "")%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","CT_NAME","A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> E group by <%=odiRef.getAKColList("", "E.[COL_NAME]", ",
		", "")%> having count(*) > 1) S where <%=odiRef.getAKColList("", "(("+odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME]=S.[COL_NAME]) or (("+odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME] is null) and (S.[COL_NAME] is null)))", "
	and	", "")%> <%=odiRef.getFilter()%>

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_ERR_TYPE, ODI_ERR_MESS, ODI_ORIGIN, ODI_CHECK_DATE, ODI_CONS_NAME, ODI_CONS_TYPE, ODI_SESS_NO, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> ) select '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=odiRef.getFK("MESS")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=odiRef.getFK("FK_NAME")%>', 'FK', '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>', <%=odiRef.getColList("", odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> <%if (odiRef.getFK("COMPLEX_SQL").equals("")) {%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%> left outer join <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "FK_PK_TABLE_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> PK on <%=odiRef.getFKColList("", odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME] =PK.[PK_COL_NAME]", "
	and	", "")%> where <%=odiRef.getFKColList("", "PK.[PK_COL_NAME] is null", "
	and	", "")%> and <%=odiRef.getFKColList("",odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME] is not null", "
and	", "")%> <%=odiRef.getFilter()%> <%}else{%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%> left outer join <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "FK_PK_TABLE_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> PK on <%=odiRef.getFK("COMPLEX_SQL")%> where <%=odiRef.getFKColList("", "PK.[PK_COL_NAME] is null", "
	and	", "")%>
<%=odiRef.getFilter()%> <%}%>

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_ERR_TYPE, ODI_ERR_MESS, ODI_ORIGIN, ODI_CHECK_DATE, ODI_CONS_NAME, ODI_CONS_TYPE, ODI_SESS_NO, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP")%> ) select '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=odiRef.getCK("MESS")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=odiRef.getCK("COND_NAME")%>', 'CK', '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>', <%=odiRef.getColList("", odiRef.getCK("COND_ALIAS") + ".[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP")%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getCK("COND_ALIAS")%> where not (<%=odiRef.getCK("COND_SQL")%>) <%=odiRef.getFilter()%>

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_ERR_TYPE, ODI_ERR_MESS, ODI_ORIGIN, ODI_CHECK_DATE, ODI_CONS_NAME, ODI_CONS_TYPE, ODI_SESS_NO, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP")%> ) select '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=odiRef.getNotNullCol("MESS")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=odiRef.getSqlQuotedString(odiRef.getNotNullCol("COL_NAME"))%>', 'NN', '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>', <%=odiRef.getColList("", odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS") + ".[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP")%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%> where <%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%>.<%=odiRef.getNotNullCol("COL_NAME")%> is null <%=odiRef.getFilter()%>

delete from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> where exists ( select 'X' from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> E <%if (odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE").equals("F")) {%> where (<%=odiRef.getColList("","(("+odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] = E.[COL_NAME]) OR ("+odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] is null AND E.[COL_NAME] is null))", "\n\tand \t", "", "UK=1")%>) <%}else{%> where (<%=odiRef.getColList("","(("+odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] = E.[COL_NAME]) OR ("+odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] is null AND E.[COL_NAME] is null))", "\n\tand \t", "", "PK=1")%>) <%}%> and (ODI_ERR_TYPE = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' and ODI_ORIGIN = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>') )
DEMO.CKM Netezza.insert check sum into check table
DEMO.CKM Netezza.delete errors from controled table
